      "rationale": "Input parameter uncertainty analysis not required at MRL 2. Nominal values for fluid density (1050 kg/m³), viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s), and rotational speed drawn from device specification and experimental protocol. Sensitivity to ±5% input variation assessed informally; NIH changes by <3%."
