      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; sample characterisation documented for traceability.",
      "rationale": "Porcine blood samples characterised for hematocrit and plasma free hemoglobin prior to each test run. Sample preparation protocol follows ASTM F1841. Formal statistical assessment of sample variability not required at MRL 2."
